{"title":"Semiologia_Disartria_Afasia-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neurología/Semiologia_Disartria_Afasia-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Abordaje Semiológico\\NDisartria vs Afasia","guid":"_iTbEPecSsO30nmEcc2-oQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Pregunta\\NClave Inicial","guid":"abUA33WJQE-loWoMbBxW0g","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"El paciente tiene ALTERACIÓN DEL HABLA o del LENGUAJE?","guid":"UFPC3Uf9SZWVn8Zcq6ZOqQ","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"HABLA (output motor) →\\NDISARTRIA / APRAXIA DEL HABLA","guid":"atzzIatjQ96EvnD7lHb2iw","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"Articulación, fonación, prosodia, resonancia","guid":"jM6YEEvwR-61hYJN-G64-A","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"Lenguaje escrito PRESERVADO","guid":"GW8s-aVqRs6uwgo3uOz5xw","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"Comprensión PRESERVADA","guid":"Qb3vEdToQmaBZAu5fy9-dw","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"LENGUAJE\\N(procesamiento\\Ncognitivo) →\\NAFASIA","guid":"00hXgFpcSMa6HenOzVKVcA","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Comprensión, denominación, repetición, lectura, escritura","guid":"TJhgcwyNRGu9h_-Kc8QCRg","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Afecta TODAS las modalidades de comunicación","guid":"WRNxAAIqQ42nneYwy28-Tw","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Incluye lenguaje de señas y sistema Braille","guid":"RMOapYlHQvm62x8Xzt-b1A","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"Test rápido diferenciador → pedir\\Nque ESCRIBA una oración compleja","guid":"2UqEkYiORfyQyacGglVxMw","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Si escribe bien y comprende → DISARTRIA (hardware dañado)","guid":"0YCVGPacSd-1ySL-zwLG9A","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"Si escritura alterada → AFASIA (software dañado)","guid":"TMb-R21uR46uf5QpkoZ3BA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"0","text":"Neuroanatomía del Lenguaje","guid":"4gJaEqebQ9yWkb5Oa9NSZg","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Hemisferio dominante","guid":"6ZvBP3iiTcKQI3jHchJDEw","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Izquierdo en >95% de diestros","guid":"WlsoxGsKSBaUUPK0iswKGg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Izquierdo en 31-70% de zurdos","guid":"4coq5lO0SZGK-o9jumSp7g","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"Lesión temprana (<6 años) → transferencia al derecho","guid":"sg4hDTy2Sd-P7dNUbc6P2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"Centros del lenguaje","guid":"zhYQDopxQhG6HjZtvQrH6g","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Área de Broca → giro frontal inferior posterior (Brodmann 44)","guid":"yTbPWZXySUSk2-ncvohYZg","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Producción del habla","guid":"XWSg9XOYTOeSec9aMPv-9w","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"Inerva neuronas motoras boca/laringe","guid":"ClPPnBSyQImbIv2nIV8-Jg","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"19","text":"Área de Wernicke → giro temporal superior posterior (Brodmann 22)","guid":"r0Xkjb8ST_ukA00215Z7MA","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Comprensión auditiva del lenguaje","guid":"oTRwAf-jTViGDuIpAH4i9Q","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"Asigna significado a las palabras","guid":"xikMwCOBSSyAhMwc9GIr9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"19","text":"Giro angular → lóbulo parietal inferior","guid":"HQbtntb_Ts-q4GASdzsHLA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Percepción del lenguaje escrito","guid":"Qf5twhWSRfmwHOWA7K1LRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"19","text":"Fascículo arcuato → conexión Broca-Wernicke","guid":"RCiihBgjQqi3cb7oXKbe2w","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"19","text":"Ínsula → articulación normal del habla","guid":"HNSiZRCCQqyFJh6KMxi1yg","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"14","text":"Modelo de doble vía","guid":"tIYxNPMWTlGeacERPz7GaQ","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Vía ventral → bilateral, temporal → comprensión auditiva","guid":"To1NzXK5T2KSfifu47gC0g","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"Vía dorsal → unilateral izq, frontotemporal → producción fluida","guid":"Om76XHaRS8yYHmI3Ld9Egg","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"14","text":"Lesiones subcorticales → mejor pronóstico que corticales","guid":"lR6acRH5QQer4UKAosxhUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación Semiológica Sistematizada","guid":"yerUaqakTH2i7gMi1W5CSA","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"1. Fluidez del habla","guid":"hwK09iXVSP26JopKvrEf2w","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Fluente → >5 palabras/frase, cadencia normal, sin esfuerzo","guid":"4LZH70nBTbKQhrWtJWY9yQ","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Wernicke, conducción, transcortical sensorial, anómica","guid":"zqnUXM26TYGJPOIkLBPytw","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"No fluente → <5 palabras/frase, esfuerzo, agramatismo","guid":"DFO2bbDKR7O1FsyXYtK2EQ","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Broca, transcortical motora, global","guid":"Ujz_q7cFT8m84q_URJJjAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"Pruebas → repetir /pa/, /ta/, /ka/ y palabras complejas (\"catástrofe\")","guid":"0eM_u5TmTxOkkFPMd3bT4w","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"34","text":"2. Comprensión","guid":"C7G_2yZbQU-P9vLNQuQGgg","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Órdenes simples → \"cierre los ojos\"","guid":"rF9Cq8I9RtmwozRcLJliHg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Órdenes complejas → \"con mano izquierda toque oreja derecha\"","guid":"fb-k3lnORHiPhbMMMGnV-A","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Órdenes que cruzan línea media","guid":"-8slc7EdRMCeYBRpS1w9Fg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"Estructuras gramaticales complejas","guid":"n2vUcjkMTPmMmJ8aCA_O0A","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"41","text":"TOKEN TEST → GOLD STANDARD","guid":"HzCkW242RPaRs4sb9pIkwQ","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Diseño → fichas de 5 colores, 2 formas, 2 tamaños","guid":"--rPng-RQH6wxkPOZgSIYQ","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"5 partes de complejidad creciente","guid":"3C1yS1eUQRyBynsASJE98A","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Parte 1 → \"toque el círculo rojo\" (forma + color)","guid":"nYHPxXFVQi-RsMD9IadY2g","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"Parte 2 → \"toque el rectángulo pequeño azul\" (+ tamaño)","guid":"wvuZy92RQi6gYN5xagy-bQ","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"Parte 3 → \"toque el círculo rojo Y el rectángulo azul\" (2 acciones)","guid":"4AykrerwTp2aEW_aOOz4Vg","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"Parte 4 → \"toque círculo pequeño blanco Y rectángulo grande verde\"","guid":"laICz-TCRPiD0sGC7nJXBA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"48","text":"Parte 5 → relaciones espaciales/temporales complejas","guid":"Cxz-JbIjQOaNYJc44bk00g","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"\"Ponga el círculo rojo ENCIMA del rectángulo azul\"","guid":"RX8mln-jThieanlYITqkyQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"\"ANTES de tocar el círculo, toque el rectángulo\"","guid":"_Xcux_bQRlS-_CjXaDbFKQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"46","text":"VENTAJA → fichas sin significado semántico → aísla comprensión sintáctica pura","guid":"VzKNUzoQTK2yrkInDXnCqg","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"46","text":"Versión reducida → 36 ítems, ~10 minutos","guid":"osuVVgP_R76paPbcxPyAMQ","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"46","text":"Sensible a afasias leves que pasan screening habitual","guid":"Zz0Tbi8gRfqAg65or9-Jig","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"41","text":"ALTERADA → Wernicke, global, transcortical sensorial","guid":"-lnWyDLuQGW5JM40tPy3rg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"41","text":"PRESERVADA → Broca, conducción, transcortical motora, anómica","guid":"4O-dqSXKQhyN-E7F6otF0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"34","text":"3. Repetición","guid":"GzRTGbllRECmlx9DsldOUw","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"\"Ni síes ni noes ni peros\" / \"El flan tiene frutillas\"","guid":"lbv0fDQnSjOTCHPpGk58bQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Secuencia → habla serial → oraciones cortas → frases largas de baja frecuencia","guid":"uNh7gY-lQsi0UO0DiPLwtg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"ALTERADA → Broca, Wernicke, conducción, global","guid":"FBlBiwSGSxCiBpAMe1Lvvw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"PRESERVADA → transcorticales (motora, sensorial, mixta), anómica","guid":"yybraAqCR-KnGHiLrHJ6dA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"61","text":"REGLA → afasias PERISILVIANAS alteran repetición","guid":"RJirO6ikTxONNllmZ96N_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"34","text":"4. Denominación","guid":"9KkYcs0XQyWkcLADCFtMRg","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Objetos reales → reloj, lápiz, botón","guid":"OPUWUps3SmmhSwjUIEpTCg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Por definición → \"instrumento para escribir\"","guid":"6XwCt1T5TGK_-Kwwkjzztg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Tipos de errores parafásicos","guid":"VMi43CiIRt-xJ1ALSSA-PA","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Semánticos → \"mesa\" por \"silla\" (sustitución por campo semántico)","guid":"-HfnnVEYQ0K6d0kqLtavvQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"Fonémicos → \"lesa\" por \"mesa\" (sustitución de fonemas)","guid":"K0lX_AbwS5OsT9VT4YR_nw","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"Neologismos → palabra inexistente","guid":"Br5pVnuHRwOFkkS_ADbWew","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"67","text":"Circunloquios → \"eso que se usa para escribir\"","guid":"Ti1dxrCxTFiS1zT43hfu7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"34","text":"5. Lectura y escritura","guid":"gvbYk8R9RbGDMjigR6HhjQ","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Lectura en voz alta + comprensión lectora","guid":"tSkskLwQSVyYxXcZdDiW7Q","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Escritura espontánea + al dictado + denominación escrita","guid":"QdmzVh54SzaqsygyacOcDg","children":[]},{"id":"78","par